*Subject:* {{ $json.subject }}
*From:* `{{ $json.from }}` · reported by {{ $json.reported_by }}
*Why:* {{ $json.score_reasons.slice(0, 3).join(' · ') }}
{{ $json.se_analysis.impersonated_entity ? '*Impersonating:* ' + $json.se_analysis.impersonated_entity : '' }}

